<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[المجرّد]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>فعَل، بفتح العين، يفعُل، بضمها<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[ب]</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[ثَقَبْتُ]</span>: الشيء ثَقْباً: أي خرقتُه.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">وثُقُوب النار والنّجوم:</span> توقُّدهما،<span class="c5"> قال اللّاه تعالى:</span> فَأَتْبَعَهُ شِهاابٌ ثااقِبٌ <span class="c2">«١»</span> أي متوقِّد من النور.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">وثُقُوب الناقة:</span> غُزْرُها.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[ل]</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[ثَقَل]</span> الشيءُ <span class="c4">[الشيءَ]</span> <span class="c2">«٢»</span> في الوزن:<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>إِذا كان أثقل منه.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>فعِل، بكسر العين، يفعَل، بفتحها<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c4">[ف]</span><a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c4">[ثَقِف]</span>: يقال: ثَقِفتُ فلاناً في الحرب:<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>أي أدركته وظفرت به،<span class="c5"> قال اللّاه تعالى:</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>فَإِمّاا تَثْقَفَنَّهُمْ فِي الْحَرْبِ <span class="c2">«٣»</span>،<span class="c5"> قال:</span> <span class="c2">«٤»</span><a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>فإِما تَثْقَفُوني فَاقْتُلُوني ... وإِنْ أَثْقَفْ فَسَوْفَ تَرَوْنَ بَالِي<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>فعُل يفعُل، بالضم فيهما<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span><span class="c4">[ف]</span><a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span><span class="c4">[ثَقُف]</span>: الثَّقافة مصدر قولك: رجل ثَقِيْف.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span><span class="c4">[ل]</span><a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span><span class="c4">[ثَقُل]</span>: الثِّقُل: نقيض الخفة، وشيء ثقيل.<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
